{"tid":264221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰謀論]海港城單案係極端組織嘅測試","createTime":"2017-05-30T15:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T03:47:15.000Z","uid":103616,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a96d2ba93e66fedef97b97d2d9376cc89a0c56b5","tid":264221,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"金正男響馬來西亞俾人殺死<br />\n係話有個女人受指使<br />\n將條有毒毛巾捂住金嘅口<br />\n仲要以為係開玩笑<br />\n<br />\n同理 響海港城單案<br />\n個放袋女人都可以係因為受指使/呃<br />\n所以將個袋丟響海港城<br />\n個女人唔會有意識有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n假設極端組織係整呢單野嘅主謀<br />\n佢地嘅目的可以係測試警方處理炸彈能力<br />\n可以係測試香港人面對恐怖襲擊嘅反應<br />\n可以係測試媒體如何處理同報導<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3644fca768489d7c8558130a5c2f94a47ec037f5","tid":264221,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"我好不安"},{"pid":"74bd2b8612d0b7f3ecba950ef4bd3b6335fcbb87","tid":264221,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"有可能試水溫"},{"pid":"31b9a03ae486d541aaba1c587b0f64cd07c1b84a","tid":264221,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95db2586014630611464afe9dd4e4d60b9751dd2","tid":264221,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"8eacde63aa722a5731a8a435e0a9a0bafb7626a5","tid":264221,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"係呀神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d9b6904d6dd5942b1286367fe3df733b9b439a","tid":264221,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"e7519934d1460db399cc509104e2f6550a870b82","tid":264221,"uid":1130